Fast-rising singer Jonzing World recording artiste, Michael Adebayo, popularly known as Ruger came through with a surprise performance for Tony Elumelu on the occasion of his birthday. The Chairman Heirs Holdings walked into the gathering of his staff who awaited his arrival at the reception. He was left utterly surprised with the emergence of Ruger with his staff who immediately began serenading him with some “Dior” goodness.   Actor Kanayo O. Kanayo curses those behind death rumour     1999 Constitution needs amendment, says Dj Big N     Ladies who pose with backsides classless – Ugezu   The excited entrepreneur was even more taken aback with the choice of song as he revealed to the singer he had just recently listened to it. Elumelu went on to enjoy the beautiful surprise performance amid cheers from his staff who captured the precious moments on their phones.